data.description:
NO LOT RENT! You own the land!The Sellers are Motivated and want to see offers! Located in the sought-after 55+ community of Laurelwood Estates you will find this very well maintained 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home.  You will be impressed when you step inside to find high ceilings, an open layout, spacious rooms, and a split bedroom floor plan. The primary bedroom offers a roomy ensuite bath with double sinks and a nicely tiled shower. The 2 additional bedrooms, which both have walk-in closets, provide plenty of space for guests or a home office.  The expansive kitchen is a cook's delight with plenty of cabinet and counter space. The newer stainless-steel appliances are just one of the added bonuses to this home. The oversized laundry room offers pantry shelves, a closet area and plenty of extra storage space. The home is also equipped with a tankless hot water system, water softener system and is tiled throughout except for 2 of the bedrooms.  The 17x16 Florida room is beautiful, giving you even more space to enjoy.  When you step outside you will find an oasis to enjoy the Florida sunshine. Whether sitting on the covered porch, relaxing in the hot tub, grilling on the open patio areas, or watching your furry friends play in the fenced yard, the options are here!  This home Is truly move in ready and just waiting for its new owners to enjoy!
With an ample sized carport, expanded driveway and 2 storage rooms with electric, you will have space for all your tools and toys.  The vinyl siding and skirting were recently replaced.  The HVAC and duct work are approx. 7 years old.  There are hurricane panels that will also convey. 
Conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, medical facilities, parks, and everything Port Orange has to offer.  This is not just a home; it's a lifestyle.  And yes, the beaches are just a short drive away!
